(42, 12, 13, 44, 8, 18, 19, 'divide the inheritance with me', 'Desire for Power and Wealth', 'This connection highlights the theme of individuals seeking power and material gain. In Luke, the request for inheritance reflects a desire for wealth, while in Acts, Simon''s offer of money demonstrates a similar pursuit of power through the Holy Spirit.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
