(42, 12, 15, 58, 13, 5, 5, 'beware of covetousness', 'Connection of Contentment and Covetousness', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of being content and warn against covetousness. Luke 12:15 states that life does not consist in possessions, while Hebrews 13:5 encourages contentment with what one has.', 'theme', 0.622, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
