(42, 12, 15, 20, 16, 16, 16, 'covetousness', 'Value of Wisdom vs. Wealth', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of wisdom and understanding over material possessions. Luke warns against covetousness, while Proverbs highlights that wisdom is better than gold.', 'theme', 0.482, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
