(42, 12, 16, 18, 12, 6, 6, 'brought forth plentifully', 'Prosperity of the Wicked', 'This connection highlights the theme of prosperity among the wealthy and those who defy God. Both passages emphasize the abundance experienced by the rich man and the robbers, suggesting a parallel in their circumstances.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
